{"tid":1461274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日一定要出黎 唔好比時間機管局諗對策","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:10:56.000Z","uid":34626,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"21b966d34198a0083ed95602c4024856e3179b9a","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"過左呢個禮拜 政府 機管局一定會諗好對策<br />\n未必再咁易搞倒機場<br />\n<br />\n琴日講過散水 聽日出黎嘅 <br />\n唔該應承左大家就要做<br />\n宜家出/放工出 都要出黎<br />\n<br />\n琴日留守覺得比人屌鬼 受委屈嘅<br />\n大家都係擔心手足安全 先嗌一齊走<br />\n宜家有多啲經驗 比多次機會 好冇？<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfac90badc93b8d91d2c4103e8e94d93acacf5fc","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b700a4cbb56db125f1a18ae33df48dbfe9982656","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2fce77e224649da4b1011b4c549fc8d30c0c67d","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8b87ffd7dab4c346b82f2a858c8ea6fa43dc7ecc","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a9eff187cbb18d854bd88f33e8a1edaff048557","tid":1461274,"uid":238444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49a3e7341492e94e787a472fdda485f13ff1ef08","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39887b98018690adf7c14bf0ee463236fa8684a7","tid":1461274,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c36501c6d1e0bab86d4efd7c1d6d1fbee0b2c8e1","tid":1461274,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-